&lt;p&gt;There are many HTML container tags, discussed in &lt;a href=&#34;dsblog/html-containers&#34;&gt;another article&lt;/a&gt;. But the content inside these container can be rendered in different ways. This is controlled by a property &lt;code&gt;display&lt;/code&gt;. What are the different values of &lt;code&gt;display&lt;/code&gt; property and what is the meaning of those, we will see those in this article.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
